videos.description: Marcus Foster hits a 3-pointer from the corner for the Bluejays in the first half vs. Providence.
videos.headline: Creighton's Foster swishes 3-pointer

videos.description: Khyri Thomas scores an easy transition layup off the feed from Mitch Ballock to cap a 9-0 run for the Bluejays.
videos.headline: Creighton's Ballock, Thomas connect for fast-break layup

videos.description: Davion Mintz hits Marcus Foster with an outlet pass, which leads to a fast-break layup and old fashion three-point play for the Bluejays.
videos.headline: Foster scores transition layup and-1

videos.description: Marcus Foster skies and slams off the full-court pass from Ty-Shon Alexander in the first half.
videos.headline: Alexander, Foster connect for dunk

videos.description: Rodney Bullock emerges from the mad scramble, and scores a layup for the Friars.
videos.headline: Providence's Bullock makes heady play for lay-in

videos.description: Khyri Thomas finds Martin Krampelj off the pick-and-roll for a dunk and old-fashion three-point play.
videos.headline: Creighton's Thomas, Krampelj execute pick-and-roll for dunk

videos.description: Marcus Foster hits a deep 3-pointer at the top of the key to give the Bluejays their largest lead of the game.
videos.headline: Foster sizes up defender and swishes deep 3-pointer

videos.description: Marcus Foster finds Martin Krampelj for a beautiful alley-oop slam dunk for the Bluejays.
videos.headline: Foster, Krampelj connect for alley-oop jam
